msgid "2) In the maven-surefire-plugin and maven-failsafe-plugin configurations, add the following `argLine` parameter:"
msgstr "2) maven-surefire-pluginおよびmaven-failsafe-plugin設定で、次の `argLine` パラメータを追加します:"

